articles.description: What do Giant Killers need in March to knock off a tournament favorite? A star performance can make a big difference. Saint Mary's Jock Landale leads our candidates to become NCAA tournament stars.

articles.description: Point guard Jahvon Quinerly, who is ranked No. 26 in the 2018 ESPN 100, has committed to Villanova. He decommitted from Arizona in October after originally pledging to the Wildcats in August.
